.row
  .col-md-9
    %p
      The purpose of this site is to compile a comprehensive database of the false reports of "hate crimes"
      committed (mostly) in the USA. It builds on the work of
      = succeed "," do
        %a{href: "/lairdwilcox"} Laird Wilcox
      whose
      %a{href: "/Crying-Wolf-by-Laird-Wilcox.pdf"} Crying Wolf
      (PDF) is the original book on this subject. The books
      %a{href: "https://www.amazon.com/Hate-Crime-Hoax-Left-Selling/dp/1621577783"} Hate Crime Hoax
      and
      %a{href: "https://www.amazon.com/Hate-Crimes-Criminal-Identity-Politics-ebook/dp/B001943QNE/"} Hate Crimes: Criminal Law & Identity Politics
      are recommended.
  .col-md-3.text-center
